## 1. Executive Summary (CEO) ðŸ‘”
> **"We are not building just a list. We are building clarity."**

The user requested a "Simple To-Do App". In the market of 10,000+ to-do apps, simplicity is the ultimate sophistication.
**Goal:** Build a frictionless, distraction-free task manager.
**Success Metric:** User adds their first task within 5 seconds of opening the app.
**Strategy:** "Less is More". No categories, no tags, no cloud sync for MVP. Local first.

