> **"Protocol 'Feature Bloat' Active: Stripping all non-essentials."**

**Target Audience:** Busy individuals who forget groceries.

### MVP Features (Phase 1)
-   [x] **Add Task:** Simple text input + "Enter".
-   [x] **List View:** Clean stream of active tasks.
-   [x] **Complete:** Tap/Swipe to check off (Satisfying micro-interaction).
-   [x] **Delete:** Swipe to remove.
-   [x] **Persist:** Data saved locally (works offline).

